              <span class="disziplin-tooltip" style="display: none; position: absolute; left: 0; transform: none; top: calc(100% + 8px); background: #1e3a8a; color: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px; font-size: 1.05em; font-weight: 400; white-space: nowrap; z-index: 99999; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); min-width: 340px; line-height: 2; pointer-events: none;">
                <strong>Score-Berechnung möglich für:</strong><br>
